* *Nihon Shoki* (Volume 1), Iwanami Bunko, 1994.
* Mitsusada, Inoue. *Myth to History*, Chūō Kōronsha, 1965.
* Kobayashi Toshio, "Mysteries of the Ancient Japanese Emperors," *History Mysteries Series 6*, Shin Jinbutsu Ōraisha, 1986.

